@page "/about"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<h2 class="about-title">Welcome to Personal Finance App</h2>

<p class="about-text">
    💰 <strong>Personal Finance App</strong> helps you manage your income and expenses with ease. Whether you're tracking daily purchases or setting long-term saving goals, this app puts you in control of your money.
</p>

<h3>🔍 Key Features</h3>
<ul class="about-list">
    <li>Track your income and expenses</li>
    <li>Set and monitor savings goals</li>
    <li>View charts and reports of your spending</li>
    <li>Manage your budget over time</li>
</ul>

<h3>📌 How to Use</h3>
<ol class="about-list">
    <li><strong>Register</strong> for an account or <strong>log in</strong> if you already have one</li>
    <li>Go to the <strong>Dashboard</strong> to add income and expenses</li>
    <li>Visit the <strong>Reports</strong> section to analyze your spending</li>
    <li>Use <strong>Goals</strong> to track your savings progress</li>
</ol>

<p class="about-text">
    🧠 Your data is stored securely and locally in the application database. We're working on future features like data export, recurring transactions, and smart insights.
</p>

